python:
sudo apt-get install idle3
python3 -m pip install sounddevice
sudo apt-get install python3-soundfile
sudo apt-get install portaudio19-dev

Arduino:
sudo git clone https://github.com/adafruit/Adafruit-PWM-Servo-Driver-Library.git
	(/usr/share/arduino/libraries)

Autoexec:
/etc/profile
	sudo chown pi /dev/tty2 (tty0, tty1, ?)
	cd robokerho
	xinit ./starter

PulseAudio:
pacmd list-sinks
pacmd set-default-sink [index|name] // Will select audio output automatically after BTConnect if set once?

Bluetooth:
bluetoothctl devices
bluetoothctl paired-devices
bluetoothctl connect [MAC:ADDRESS]

MPI3508:
git clone https://ww.github.com/goodtft/LCD-show.git
chmod -R 755 LCD-show
sudo dpkg -i xinput-calibartor...

UI:
sudo python -m pip install pysimplegui
(muista k채ynnist채채 python3.x:ll채)

UI starter script:
https://raspberrypi.stackexchange.com/questions/98944/launch-a-gui-tkinter-program-on-boot
	(starter script OK, don't use crontab -e)
